   learning, hobby, or non-commercial purposes.

   "Commercial Use" means any use of the Software in connection with an
   Organization, a business, revenue-generating activity, paid service, or
   product, or any use that is not Personal Use.

   "Small Team Limit" means five (5) Licensed Developers within a single
   Organization.

   "Authorized Copy" means a copy of the Software obtained directly from
   Licensor or through an authorized distribution channel designated by
   Licensor.

   "Commercial License Agreement" means a separate written agreement with
